creator: Lincoln Avenue Baptist Church Ministries
descriptionHtml: This app will help you stay connected with the day-to-day life of our church. With this app you can: watch or listen to past messages; stay up to date with push notifications; share your favorite messages via Twitter, Facebook, or email; and download messages for offline listening.
descriptionShort: The LABC Church App serves to connect the church.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added support for Android 12
- If enabled, Subsplash Messaging notifications now displays the sender’s avatar on Android 11+
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements
